				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${E}_{\,{{\mathrm{g}}}}^{{{\mathrm{expt}}}\,}$$\end{document} values are optical band gaps, while the GW method measures the fundamental band gaps. As discussed, the Egfund\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
